le, do you like it or not?<br>
Trewa is a world very similar to ours, but they are living in Medieval times. In that world there are many different cultures. There are three distinct parts of this world. One only knows day, Nichi is its name, the other only knows night, Getsu is its name and finally there is a part which knows both, Hitsuki is its name. Rismay is a boy who lives in Nichi. His past has been shrouded with mystery. As a child, only five, a group of knights came looking for him, but hi parents had hid him well, for an unknown reason. When his parents told the knights that Rismay had died at the age of two, they slaughtered his parents while Rismay managed to see from where he was hidden. After the knights left, Rismay took off into the forest. When he entered the forest he ran into another boy who was 15 at the time, his name was Nutamo. <br>
<br>
This next part is the first episode of my manga<br>
<br>
At the time of the story this story, Rismay is 15 and Nutamo is 25, he is living in a thick forest, close to a town named Fukuka. He has just completed his final task to show Nutamo that he is ready to be a professional thief, like Nutamo. Nutamo sends him on his first assignment, which is to rob the richest person in Fukuka. Rismay accepts and goes in for the steal. While inside he goes though the persons own library and notices a small golden book. Without hesitance he takes it and moves on to the treasury. He notices two guards outside, so he goes or the old throw a stone in the opposite direction trick. As the guards go to kill whatever it was that made the noise he stealthy runs into the treasury. When inside he gets two more golden items, a sword and a big diamond. When he is about to exit he notices that he didn?t cols the door of the treasury, big mistake. Now they knew that someone was inside. When he opens the door ten guards are waiting for him. They quickly charge at him, but he tells them to stop or he will drop the diamond that he just picked up. They all panic and then Nutamo throws it in the air, jumps over the guards as they all dive for the diamond. And safely escapes the room. <br>
